Undeploying your Alliance Starbase will remove it from its current location. You will need to spend Alliance Reserves to deploy your Alliance Starbase.

While undeployed, the Alliance Starbase may not be Assaulted, will not harvest Plasma and cannot start building or upgrading modules. Additionally, Alliance Members may not Assault other Alliance Starbases.
